The Tripredicus council first looked at Motormaster, then sneered as
they noticed Switchblade and Beastbox. "What's going on" one of the
members says. All Motormaster can do, is react, he quickly draws out his
sword, and plants it straight into the computer consol. He erupts into a
burst of electircal discharge as the screen begins to fade. Motormaster
looks back up, "We are having some technical difficult..." he is cut off
by the screen failing. He breaths a sigh of relief.

The Tripredicus council look at each other, a bit perplexed, as to what
had just happened. "Could it be that there is, much more going on than
meets the eye." he finishes. Reflector reenters with a box in one of his
hands, and another one is carrying a large gourney.
